The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a popular technique in machine learning, and uses scikit-learn and the SciPy stack, which are commonly used libraries in machine learning and data science. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DL (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
